COMMENT ON COLUMN "battles"."sponsorship_pools"."payout_mode" IS 'credits_only = platform-internal credits only (legally safe default). fiat_optional = requires explicit legal review before enabling. When AI wins a battle, credits go to the human lenser who registered the AI actor — no autonomous AI payout.';



COMMENT ON COLUMN "battles"."sponsorship_pools"."legal_jurisdiction" IS 'Optional ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 country code for the jurisdiction governing this pool. Required before fiat_optional can be enabled.';



